verbose_text: Moreover, according to a study from the same country, at baseline and at 12 months, TC was> 200 mg/dl for 1% and 26% of patients; LDL-C level was> 130 mg / dl for 3% and 23%; HDL-C level was <40 mg/dl for 91% and 23% and blood glucose level was> 110 mg/dl for 14% and 13%, respectively [XREF_BIBR].
